DESCRIPTION

  App::Xssh
    This program will allow you to ssh to a remote host inside a new
    X Terminal window (like XTerm).  


PREREQUISITES

  App::Xssh requires at least perl 5.6.0 and these other modules and libraries:

    Config::General
    X1::Terminal


BUILDING/INSTALLING

  Once the archive is unpacked, use these commands:

      perl Makefile.PL
      make
      make test
      make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

  Please send any feedback to the author: egiles@cpan.org

  See 'Changes' for a detailed history.

  See perldoc App::Xssh


